## Sibling repos

The two `datetime.ts` helpers are intentionally portable. When this
file is mirrored into REMICustomer, REMIDashboard, or REMIBackend,
the function signatures stay identical so behavior matches across
producers. If you change a signature, change it everywhere in the
same PR.
